snippet.title: Demeo | PC Edition - Wishlist Now on Steam
snippet.description:
Grab your friends and assemble a party, because Demeo: PC Edition is bringing its cooperative, four-player adventure to Steam Early Access on April 7! This award-winning multiplayer game of virtual tabletop tactics has been completely rebuilt for a native PC experience, and will include every Demeo adventure released to date — with the promise to deliver all future adventures simultaneously across all available platforms.

Wishlist here: https://reso.ly/3s7oYCh
https://resolutiongames.com/demeo
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DemeoGame
Discord: https://discord.gg/jAxYStqsUD
#Demeo #steam #ResolutionGames #RPG
